Key Match Events: South Africa eliminated from T20 World Cup
Brandon Glover returned impressive figures of 3-9 in two overs
Colin Ackermann's unbeaten 41 was the highest score for Netherlands
Pre-Game Insights: South Africa was expected to comfortably beat Netherlands
Post-Match Reflections: Temba Bavuma: 'Hard one to swallow. We had the confidence and belief in ourselves as a unit to make the play-offs, unfortunately for us, we couldn't do it'
Scott Edwards: 'Lost for words. It's definitely up there, another big upset for Netherlands in a World Cup'
Colin Ackermann: 'Feels fantastic, we really deserved this victory. Boys worked really hard. Come in, and take it deep, and the boundaries flowed at the end'
Miscellaneous Highlights: This loss leaves Bangladesh and Pakistan fighting it out for the final spot in the last four
Others: The match was played at Adelaide Oval in Adelaide, Australia
